          "date": "2019-07-14 11:56:17.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-12400 ldiskfs: Case insensitive dirhash ext4fs_dirhash",
        "message": "LU-12400 ldiskfs: Case insensitive dirhash ext4fs_dirhash\n\nExt4 added case-insensitive (per directory) support.\nThis change affects the directory hashing scheme so that\non case-insensitive flagged directories the mixed case\nnames hash to the same value.\n\nThis patch updates the API call but does not support the\ncase-insensitive flagged directory scheme.\n\nLinux-commit: 8a363970d1dc38c4ec4ad575c862f776f468d057\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nCray-bug-id: LUS-7600\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <stancheff@cray.com>\nChange-Id: Ia358e52d1ea7efad5984c4657a07a8ef2d35915e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
